---
---

<section id="about" class="py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">

  <div class="mb-16">
    <span class="section-label" data-i18n="about.label">ABOUT</span>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">

    <!-- Decorative type element — large text clips to create editorial effect -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center py-10 fade-in">
      <span
        class="text-[10rem] md:text-[14rem] font-black font-headline leading-none select-none"
        style="color: #474552;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >About</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Bio text -->
    <div class="fade-in">
      <p
        class="font-mono text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed"
        style="color: #e8e4dc;"
        data-i18n="about.bio"
      >
        Angular engineer by trade, builder by nature. I've shipped production-grade frontends
        for Disney, Royal Caribbean, and United Airlines — and I bring that same standard to
        every freelance project I take on. Originally from Monterrey, now based in Houston.
        When I'm not coding, I'm gaming, learning something new, or prototyping the next idea.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

</section>
